{"tid":1721482,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[勿捉鬼] 關於大學出入check袋問題 唔希望呢種風氣繼續廣散","createTime":"2019-11-14T16:11:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T16:16:54.000Z","uid":69525,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c48133cab74444680c832b1e33b718a61010e788","tid":1721482,"uid":69525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:11:21.000Z","msg":"我明大家驚有便衣狗藍絲混入<br />\n係入口check袋check證<br />\n但有無諗過check人果個都未必安全<br />\n今日見到話poly一直都話要人<br />\n但入到poly又要check又盛 又話唔要人<br />\n最重要既係 check袋隨身物品都算<br />\n仲check埋學生證 工作證 乜比人睇哂 <br />\n咁到底遮面黎有咩用<br />\n<br />\n我真心唔希望呢種check袋check證既壞風氣廣散<br />\n特別係每次現場都總有班死左膠捉鬼<br />\n咁鐘意捉鬼<br />\n<br />\n提防有鬼 但請勿亂捉鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62aa88c9b2f3ff5996422f025f34226ad76fc360","tid":1721482,"uid":69525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:12:25.000Z","msg":"擴散<br />\n擴散<br />\n擴散<br />\n打錯字 屌"},{"pid":"4a84d7c31fc208ceea1b668bd3027ff2d0468826","tid":1721482,"uid":17360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:13:19.000Z","msg":"借個位<br />\n希望大家可以幫手推下<br />\n<br />\n機會嚟啦文宣組<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1721163\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1721163</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"cd33190020cd0ec9e46233283d1401fd3fc922f7","tid":1721482,"uid":264245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:14:51.000Z","msg":"講撚左好多次，勿捉鬼"},{"pid":"203553992fa104f3dcad92f5c4716446c32dc199","tid":1721482,"uid":264245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:15:42.000Z","msg":"2014年輸d乜，自己諗下<br />\n<br />\n就算今年先開始醒，講捉鬼都唔輪到你地話捉就捉"},{"pid":"557ad2a7c655fd5376f404bc7572bef8ab32c0b3","tid":1721482,"uid":309045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:16:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/norm